OL,5,G1930 Bradley & Barney Walsh: Breaking
OL,6,G     Dad
OL,7,     FBradley and Barney arrive in
OL,8,     FBrisbane, where they swap the RV
OL,9,     Ffor electric scooters to explore
OL,10,     Fthe city. The pair head to the
OL,11,     Flocal racetrack, where they go
OL,12,     Fhead to head in a sport known to
OL,13,     Fthe locals as 'the trots', and end
OL,14,     Fthe day with a group who gather
OL,15,     Fevery week to immerse themselves
OL,16,     Fin medieval fantasy role-play.
OL,17,     FThey also meet a man who went
OL,18,     Fviral thanks to a very unexpected
OL,19,     Ftalent, before Barney plans
OL,20,     Fanother adrenaline-fuelled treat
OL,21,     Ffor his dad
